Package: ggpointgrid
Title: Rearrange scatter plot points on a regular grid
Description: A simple geom (geom_pointgrid) derived from geom_point that rearranges the input points for a scatterplot on a regular grid while strictly avoiding over-plotting.
Version: 1.0.0
